          <div class="news-article" id="article2">

            <div class="news-header">

              <div class="title-container">
                <p class="news-title">
                  Voting is now OPEN for the 6th Annual Designer Toy Awards!
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="date-container">
                <p class="news-date">
                  09/19/2016
                </p>
              </div>

            </div>

            <div class="news-img">
              <img src="assets/images/NewsImg2.jpg" alt="">
            </div>


            <p class="news-text">
              Thank you everyone, for all of the amazing nominations for the 6th Annual Designer Toy Awards! Our nomination committees worked tirelessly to whittle down the 100’s of nominees and finally we are happy to announce the shortlist of FINALISTS!
              <br><br>
              We would like to take this opportunity to sincerely thank our committees for all their hard work, they really go above any beyond to meet daily and discuss each and every category and entry in depth! Believe us when I tell you, every aspect was discussed.
              <br><br>
              Pro Committee: Jackson Aw, Huck Gee, Dov Kelemer, Kirby Kerr, Benny Kline, Travis Lykins, Gary Rozanski, John Stokes, and Vincnt Yu.
              <br><br>
              Public: Justin Cheah , Lee Funai, Ketha Insomphou, Steve Lew, Rob Lumino, and Katherine Park
              <br><br>
              Together, they created our Shortlists of 2016! Congratulations to all the finalists!
              <br><br>
              And now it is up to you–yes, you!–to vote on the best of 2015! Voting in the DTA public categories is easy as cake. Just follow these steps:
              <br><br>
              Log in or create a new account above. If you have an account but have forgotten the password, you can retrieve it here.
              Go to the categories page.
              Vote once in each of the six awards under Public Voting.
              <br><br>
              Tada! You've voted! Simple as that.
              <br><br>
              Public voting remains open until Monday, Sept, 26th at 12 (noon) est! So hurry and submit your votes before it's too late!
              <br><br>
              Happy voting!
              Please note that voting more than once in each category, even if you've created multiple accounts, is grounds for all your votes being removed and, potentially, the party you're voting for being disqualified.
            </p>
